{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, in this context, our work can serve as a foundation for future automated summarization from scientific papers, and further contributing to research on review generation.",
    "This paper has several limitations.",
    "Firstly, our proposed two-stage framework for abstractive summarization of scientific articles, which includes two sequential tasks:",
    "structural function recognition and abstractive summarization, may introduce potential errors in task transmission.",
    "Secondly, while we applied PLMs like BART, PEGASUS, T5, and Longformer for abstractive summarization, we did not fine-tune them specifically to the arXiv and PubMed datasets."
  ]
}